| <span class=""prop-name"">Alert-Outlined</span> | Styles applied to the root element if `Variant=""@AlertVariant.Outlined""`.
| <span class=""prop-name"">Alert-Standard</span> | Styles applied to the root element if `Variant=""@AlertVariant.Standard""`.
