| <span class=""prop-name"">Alert-Filled-Warning</span> | Styles applied to the root element if `Variant=""@AlertVariant.Filled""` and `Color=""@Color.Warning""`.
| <span class=""prop-name"">Alert-Filled-Error</span> | Styles applied to the root element if `Variant=""@AlertVariant.Filled""` and `Color=""@Color.Error""`.
| <span class=""prop-name"">Alert-Icon</span> | Styles applied to the icon wrapper element.
| <span class=""prop-name"">Alert-Message</span> | Styles applied to the message wrapper element.
| <span class=""prop-name"">Alert-Action</span> | Styles applied to the action wrapper element if `action` is provided.

